when I think about it.

00:02:41.536 --> 00:02:43.621 position:50% align:center
- How did the hearing
with S.A.R.G. go?

00:02:44.289 --> 00:02:48.001 position:50% align:center
- Uh, let's just say I never
wanna go through that again.

00:02:48.084 --> 00:02:50.837 position:50% align:center
- So, you chased your dog
that kept running away

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:52.964 position:50% align:center
