on the train tracks?

00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:55.050 position:50% align:center
- Yes.

00:02:55.133 --> 00:02:56.718 position:50% align:center
- You know this person, correct?

00:02:56.801 --> 00:02:57.886 position:50% align:center
- Uh--
[stammers]

